						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndra. Year 6: A.D. 1069.</hi></p>						

						<p>Unfinished. Mentions the mercantile body <hi rend="italic">(Nagarattār)</hi> of Kōmaḷam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīrachōḻa-paṭṭinam in Paḍuvur-nāḍu, a subdivision of Āmūr-kōṭṭam. The village Kōmaḷam could be identified with Kōvaḷam, a village situated north of Tiruvaḍandai.</p>						

